{"tid":2171619,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[保護自己既DNA,專家食屎]負責全港檢驗既集團 華大集團 係被美國制裁既企業之一","createTime":"2020-08-24T05:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T01:41:26.000Z","uid":54623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f94bf21bfdbcf1030875d41d43246153850625","tid":2171619,"uid":54623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:28:32.000Z","msg":"2020年7月14日既新聞<br />\n【Now新聞台】政府接觸兩間內地私營機構為本港進行新冠病毒檢測。據了解，分別是<span class=\"red\">華大基因</span>及中國檢驗認證集團。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">華大基因</span>的廠房位於大埔，有工人搬運紙箱，負責人於電話未有否認將與政府合作驗新冠病毒，但要求記者書面查詢。<br />\n------------------<br />\n2020-07-22 HK01新聞<br />\n日前，新疆絲路<span class=\"red\">華大基因</span>科技有限公司和北京六合華大基因科技有限公司被美國商務部列入出口管制「實體清單」的11間企業當中，其被指控涉嫌強制採集維吾爾人基因研究。<br />\n<br />\n深圳<span class=\"red\">華大基因</span>股份有限公司（簡稱<span class=\"red\">華大基因</span>）21日晚發佈公吿，對其下屬子公司新疆絲路<span class=\"red\">華大基因</span>科技有限公司和北京六合<span class=\"red\">華大基因</span>科技有限公司被美國商務部列入實體清單一事進行說明，表示會盡最大努力消除不利影響，又強調該公司恪守商業倫理，嚴格遵守國際商業慣例及法律法規。<br />\n---------------<br />\n8月24日now新聞<br />\n<br />\n中大生物醫學院副教授<span class=\"red\">李天立</span>：：「唾液或其他鼻咽細胞量太少，我們會加大一倍(PCR循環)，做不做到？是可行的，但質素，即基因圖譜的質素一定會差，可能圖譜完成時，有5%或10至20%錯誤率。以影印為例，每影印一次，雜訊就多了。」<br />\n<br />\n他指出，若化驗所收到的樣本，無法識別市民身分，涉及私隱風險較低，但政府應公開化驗所處理樣本的指引。<br />\n-------------<br />\n<span class=\"red\">李天立</span><br />\n<br />\n    香港中文大學醫學院生物醫學學院副教授<br />\n    香港生物科技協會副主席<br />\n   <span class=\"red\"> 華大集團</span>香港科學顧問<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:9tflK-bdzwAJ:https://www.bio-hk.com/index.php/zh/about-us/organising-committee/71-lee-tin-lap-jp+&amp;cd=5&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ct=clnk&amp;gl=hk&amp;client=firefox-b-d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebcache.googleusercontent.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dcache%3A9tflK-bdzwAJ%3Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bio-hk.com%2Findex.php%2Fzh%2Fabout-us%2Forganising-committee%2F71-lee-tin-lap-jp%2B%26cd%3D5%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26ct%3Dclnk%26gl%3Dhk%26client%3Dfirefox-b-d&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=e0259dc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:9tflK-bdzwAJ:https://www.bio-hk.com/index.php/zh/about-us/organising-committee/71-lee-tin-lap-jp+&amp;cd=5&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ct=clnk&amp;gl=hk&amp;client=firefox-b-d</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=402888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402888&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=115c95ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402888&h=11e8cbe8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=402888</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=397890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397890&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=1b8389f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397890&h=c02a93f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=397890</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/501131/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E4%BE%B5%E7%8A%AF%E7%B6%AD%E6%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A-%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D-%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E6%81%AA%E5%AE%88%E5%95%86%E6%A5%AD%E5%80%AB%E7%90%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F501131%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E7%258A%25AF%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%2597%258F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2581%25AA%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%2580%25AB%25E7%2590%2586&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkq